results.title: Laugh Love Live Tile Trivet Decorative Coaster Inspirational Tile Motivational Gift for Encouragement for Hard Times - Tile with Easel
results.description:
Our "Laugh as Much as You Breath, Love as Much as You Live" decorative tile is a great way to add some motivation to your daily space.  And a great gift to anyone needing a little encouragement or a reminder to stay positive!  


These tiles are one of our favorite things in our shop!  Always popular with customers at our local fairs, there's sure to be a design (or two!) that's perfect for your home.  And they make absolutely great gifts - teachers, coworkers, friends, moms, dads, new neighbors, coaches....the list is endless!  

The tile measures about 4" square.  The printed paper has been adhered to the top of the tile.  It has a stiff felt backing to protect furniture and has been sealed for durability.  Not recommended for hot dishes or the dishwasher, but easily cleaned with a damp cloth. 

The accompanying easel is the perfect way to display your tile.  The black wood is a neutral that would coordinate well with any décor.  It measures about 5.5" tall.  

Sending directly as a gift?  Just let us know and we'd be happy to do a complimentary gift wrap for you!


Don't forget we can customize any tile for you!  We love getting convos from folks who are looking to add a personal touch. We can add names, dates and quotes to our existing designs, or start from scratch by using your photos, artwork, logos, memorabilia - really anything you can dream up!  We love to help make things just perfect for you.  And we also do custom quantities, so if you need a certain amount let us know and we can get you the right price.  


Be sure to visit our shop at www.etsy.com/shop/PeppercornPrincess to find more great coasters and other happy ideas like this!
